high_descs: Turn around and move left to the toaster.
Take the bowl out of the cabinet on the top left.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Wash the bowl in the sink.
Open the counter on the top left and place the bowl inside of it, to the right of the red container.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed bowl in a cabinet.

high_descs: Step back from the sink, turn right and walk across the kitchen, turn right and face the counter.
Open the cupboard above your head and get the bowl
Turn around to the right and carry the bowl to the sink
Turn the sink on and fill the bowl with water
Turn around to the left, carry the bowl back to the counter, and raise it up to the cupboard
Put the bowl in the cupboard
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl of water into the cupboard

high_descs: Turn right, walk the toaster on the counter to your right and look up to the cabinet.
Grab the bowl inside the cabinet.
Turn right and walk to the sink to your right.
Fill the bowl up with water and grab the bowl.
Turn left, a quick left again and look up to the cabinet.
Place the bowl filled with water next to the red vase in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl filled with water next to the red vase in the cabinet.
